data_table.description: Cardiac MRI Wall Motion Abnormality, Offspring Cohort 2002 - 2006

variable.name: wmsi
variable.description: GLOBAL WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (THIS SHOULD EQUAL WMS VALUE DIVIDED BY 17)

variable.name: antwmsi
variable.description: ANTERIOR WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (ANTERIOR WMS DIVIDED BY 3)

variable.name: sepwmsi
variable.description: SEPTAL WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (SEPTAL WMS DIVIDED BY 5)

variable.name: infwmsi
variable.description: INFERIOR WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (INFERIOR WMS DIVIDED BY 3)

variable.name: latwmsi
variable.description: LATERAL WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (LATERAL WMS DIVIDED BY 5)

variable.name: basewmsi
variable.description: BASE WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (BASE WMS DIVIDED BY 6)

variable.name: midwmsi
variable.description: MIDWALL WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (MIDWALL WMS DIVIDED BY 6)

variable.name: apexwmsi
variable.description: APEX WALL MOTION SCORE INDEX (APEX WMS DIVIDED BY 5)

variable.name: date
variable.description: CARDIAC MRI SCAN DATE, NUMBER OF DAYS SINCE EXAM 1
